## Daily Startup Checklist

1. Check Discord `#dev-chat` for new messages and @ mentions
2. Check GitHub notifications: `gh api notifications --jq '.[].subject.title'`
3. Review open PRs awaiting your review: `gh pr list --assignee @me`
4. Check your assigned issues: `gh issue list --assignee @me --state open`
5. Scan for high-priority unassigned work:
   ```bash
   gh issue list --repo infiquetra/<repo> --assignee "" --state open --label "P0"
   ```

